Watch Live: Donald Trump Speaks at a MAGA Rally in Louisiana | Breitbart
07 Nov 2019, 01:20 by Charlie Spiering
President Donald Trump will speak at a campaign rally in Louisiana on Wednesday.
The president is expected to speak at 8:00 p.m. EST.
